<mvc:View controllerName="ns.sapui5.controller.HelloPanel" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" id="_IDGenView2" displayBlock="true">
    <Panel id="_IDGenPanel1" headerText="{i18n>helloPanel}" class="sapUiResponsiveMargin" width="auto">
        <content>
            <Text id="_IDGenText1" text="Nombre" />

            <Input id="_IDGenInput1" value="{/recipient/name}" />
            <Button id="_IDGenButton2" 
                    icon="sap-icon://address-book" 
                    text="{i18n>showHelloDialog}" 
                    press=".onOpenDialog" 
                    class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd" />
            <Button id="_IDGenButton1" text="{i18n>showHelloButtonText}" press=".onShowHello" class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd" />
            <Input id="_IDGenInput2" value="{/recipient/city}" valueLiveUpdate="true" width="60%" />
            <Text id="_IDGenText2" text="Bienvenido a {/recipient/city}" class="sapUiSmallMargin boldElements sapthemeHighlight-asColor" />
        </content>
    </Panel>
    <!-- se carga fragmento Form01-->
    <core:Fragment fragmentName="ns.sapui5.view.Form01" type="XML" />
</mvc:View>
